  "description": "A smiling woman in autumnal clothing poses in front of a vibrant yellow tree. She is wearing a knitted orange beanie, a soft grey sweater, and a peach-colored shawl draped around her shoulders. Her hair is wavy and light brown. She rests her chin on a grey stone ledge, gazing directly at the camera with a warm and inviting expression. The background is dominated by the dense, golden foliage of a tree in full autumn color. The sky is a bright, clear blue.  The scene is well-lit with natural daylight. A lamppost and a green street sign are faintly visible in the far background.",
